	<h1 class="title">3个月了，神剧《古剑奇谭》为什么还没招人烦？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/999/small/999.jpg?1404052188" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陆云霏</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-09-24 10:23:06 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2525/medium/2525.jpg?1436651896" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


